  I know I have posted numerous times about my gear.  I was wondering if anyone can give thier opinions about what i need to change.  I am trying to get ready for the planes so I am swapping some ac for HP and STA items.  Hopefully soon I can start my Thurg armor but that is going to be slow going due to the fact I got to rely on Kael raids for the drops.  Here is my Magelo the AC is a little bit screwy so i dont think it is right.  Thank you for your help in advance.<br>
